        201("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Job: houba-scan-attach</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Infrastructure Node: Kubernetes Job]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>Two off-the-shelf analyzers,<br />agnostic (houba keys on SARIF<br />result.kind, not the tool):<br />grype evaluates the SBOM<br />referrer (grype sbom:, no<br />creds; vuln.* => SCAN), regis<br />analyzes the placed image<br />(governance:<br />EOL/hygiene/licenses;<br />policy.* => POLICY). houba<br />attach binds each SARIF as a<br />signed referrer on the same<br />digest (two<br />referrers/digest). regctl +<br />grype + regis + houba, no<br />derived image. grype pulls<br />its CVE DB; regis pulls the<br />image + its analyzer data<br />(air-gapped => mirror).</div>")
